# Personal persona definitions for the dogfood-agent app. The app code +
# the generic `new-user.md` persona ship; user-specific personas (with
# real names, employers, life context) stay local. Drop additional .md
# files into apps/dogfood-agent/personas/ — they'll be picked up by the
# loader without being tracked.
apps/dogfood-agent/personas/kevin-weekday.md

